<HL>
   Salomon to Pay
   $83.8 Million
   On Oil Claims
   ----
   By Michael Siconolfi
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/12/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C10
</SO>
